'''史蒂芬·廣之·青木'''（{{Lang-en|Steven Hiroyuki Aoki}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=ABOUT US {{!}} SVN sound by Steve Aoki|url=https://www.svnsound.jp/about-us|access-date=2021-10-19|work=SVNsound|language=ja|archive-date=2022-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220314200538/https://www.svnsound.jp/about-us|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{Bd|1977年|11月30日}}）是一名美國DJ、音樂製作人、音樂程式師、音樂總監<ref>{{Cite web|title=DIM MAK :: bands :: Kid Millionaire|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040824011450/http://www.dimmak.com/kidmillionaire/|access-date=2021-10-19|date=2004-08-24|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>、以及生前經營[[Benihana|Benihana]]加盟連鎖餐廳的他的父親[[青木廣彰|青木廣彰]]的財產繼承人<ref>{{Cite web|title=Aoki v. Aoki, 985 N.Y.S.2d 523 {{!}} Casetext Search + Citator|url=https://casetext.com/case/aoki-v-aoki-1|access-date=2021-10-19|work=casetext.com|archive-date=2021-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211021080758/https://casetext.com/case/aoki-v-aoki-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年，《{{link-en|Pollstar|Pollstar}}》指定史蒂夫·青木是北美巡演票房最高的[[電子舞曲|電子舞曲]]藝人<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pollstar’s Mid-Year Charts & Figures {{!}} Pollstar|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004083902/http://www.pollstar.com/news_article.aspx?ID=802058|access-date=2021-10-19|date=2012-10-04|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>。他曾和[[蔡依林|蔡依林]]、 [[威廉_(歌手)|will.i.am]]、[[艾佛傑克|Afrojack]]、[[笑本部|LMFAO]]、[[聯合公園|Linkin Park]]、[[伊基·阿塞莉娅|Iggy Azalea]]、[[利尔·乔恩|Lil Jon]]、[[眨眼182|blink-182]]、{{link-en|Laidback Luke|Laidback Luke}}、[[防彈少年團|BTS]]、[[MONSTA_X|Monsta X]]、[[路易·湯姆林森|Louis Tomlinson]]、[[後街男孩|Backstreet Boys]]、{{link-en|Rise Against|Rise Against}}、{{link-en|Vini Vici|Vini Vici}}、{{link-en|Lauren Jauregui|Lauren Jauregui}}、[[打倒男孩|Fall Out Boy]], [[艾倫·沃克|Alan walker]]等藝人合作，同時憑藉為[[Kid_Cudi|Kid Cudi]]等藝人重混的作品聞名。史蒂夫·青木也曾發行許多上榜《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》的錄音室專輯，包括曾在2013年入圍[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]{{link-en|最佳電子/舞曲專輯|Grammy Award for Best Dance/Electronic Album}}的《{{link-en|Wonderland|Wonderland (Steve Aoki album)}}》。他是史蒂夫·青木慈善基金的創始人，為全球人道主義救濟組織籌集資金。2019年，史蒂夫·青木出版了一部回憶錄《Blue: The Color of Noise》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Steve Aoki Announces Memoir 'BLUE: The Color of Noise' (Exclusive)|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8500303/steve-aoki-memoir-blue-the-color-of-noise|access-date=2021-10-19|work=Billboard|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020053810/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8500303/steve-aoki-memoir-blue-the-color-of-noise|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=DJ Mag Unveils Top 101-150 DJs: Sasha, Arty, Flosstradamus, Flume, Jamie Jones Ranked|url=https://www.musictimes.com/articles/51759/20151021/dj-mag-unveils-top-101-150-djs-sasha-arty-flosstradamus-flume-jamie-jones.htm|access-date=2021-10-19|date=2015-10-21|last=Middleton|first=Ryan|work=Music Times|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020232739/https://www.musictimes.com/articles/51759/20151021/dj-mag-unveils-top-101-150-djs-sasha-arty-flosstradamus-flume-jamie-jones.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

